      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking reliability and comfort without the new-car price tag. The exterior presents beautifully, finished in a deep metallic coat that still catches the light; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway use, the body is straight and free of any significant dings. Inside, the cabin has been kept in impressive shape. The upholstery is clean and firm, the dashboard is free of sun damage, and every electronic component\u2014from the infotainment screen to the heated seats\u2014operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the car has been treated with care, benefiting from a documented history of synthetic oil changes and recent brake service. It drives straight, shifts smoothly, and the tires have plenty of tread remaining for the seasons ahead. Smoke-free and garage-kept, this car is ready for immediate daily use.",
      "price": 32500.0,
